---
description: Guidelines when identifying and fixing bugs.
alwaysApply: false
---
- Create a repdouction unit test before fixing a bug.
- Run tests liberally.
- Add debug statements liberally while debugging.
- Use tools and temporary code changes actively to understand the bug.
- Mark temporary changes during the debug process with comments.
- Clean up the debug statements and temporary changes during the debug process after it has been fixed.
